{
    "AIF": {
        "nodes": [
            {
                "nodeID": "iss1",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "Should ministers accept the Industrial Injuries Advisory Council's recommendations?"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_iss1",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "Ministers must now decide whether to accept IIAC\u2019s recommendations"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_iss1",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "pos1",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "The Department for Work and Pensions is carrying out a detailed assessment of the report's recommendations."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_pos1",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "the Department for Work and Pensions (DWP) was carrying out a detailed assessment of the report\u2019s recommendations"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_pos1",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "iss2",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "Should long covid be included as a prescribed disease?"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_iss2",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "Debate about including long covid as a prescribed disease"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_iss2",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "pos2",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "The Industrial Injuries Advisory Council considered that there was not sufficient evidence to recommend general prescription for long covid or post-Covid syndrome."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_pos2",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "IIAC therefore considered there was not sufficient evidence at that time to recommend general prescription for long covid/post-Covid syndrome"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_pos2",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "arg1",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "Current understanding of the underlying pathophysiology, temporal course, and predictable effects of the key symptoms of post-Covid syndrome is limited, and the ability to diagnose the condition objectively is also limited."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_arg1",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "current understanding of the underlying pathophysiology, temporal course, and predictable effects of the key symptoms of Post-COVID syndrome is limited, as is the ability to diagnose the condition objectively"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_arg1",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "pos3",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "The Council is unable to recommend prescription for long covid at this time."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_pos3",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "the Council is unable to recommend prescription for this condition at this time"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_pos3",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "iss3",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "Is there a need for greater recognition and support for long covid?"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_iss3",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "Calls for greater recognition and support for long covid"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_iss3",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "pos4",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "Patients, charities, and healthcare professionals believe there is a need for greater recognition and awareness of long covid, as well as better access to medical assessments and support."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_pos4",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "Patients, charities and health care professionals have raised concerns about recognition and awareness of long covid, and difficulties in accessing appropriate medical assessments and support"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_pos4",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "arg2",
                "type": "I",
                "text": "A report highlighted a lack of awareness and knowledge of the condition and support services among GPs, mixed experiences of long covid clinics, and a lack of holistic support."
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "l_0_arg2",
                "type": "L",
                "text": "The report highlighted a lack of awareness and knowledge of the condition and support services amongst GPs, mixed experience of long Covid clinics and a lack of holistic support"
            },
            {
                "nodeID": "ya_0_arg2",
                "type": "YA",
                "text": "Default Illocuting"
            },
